{"tid":1375492,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］奪權","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T08:58:26.000Z","uid":31738,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84c947a2b89b1ebf4bd8c89ae0bd45fee975810c","tid":1375492,"uid":31738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"本來無咩立場，但呢個時候唔係講黃藍絲<br />\n係講事非黑白，你當我藍絲都好<br />\n<br />\n成個政府架空左除左出稿譴責無人回應<br />\n警方屌政務司司長出黎降溫<br />\n<br />\n相反每次有事發生，警方都是第一時間回應<br />\n宜家比人感覺警察取代政府決定社會日後發展方向<br />\n好似奪權變左軍伐政府咁<br />\n<br />\n有無理解錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錯請有理據狠狠地屌<br />\n<br />\n無錯的話麻煩文宣組幫手宣傳<br />\n整埋英文比外國媒體 <br />\n歡迎全世界一齊理性討論"},{"pid":"6abf04371c00e481cf5eaa3ec79d9a7a6ecc3d0a","tid":1375492,"uid":31738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"歡迎理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f25ecea45864412859db99726f314347d31ff2b","tid":1375492,"uid":31738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"歡迎理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b85b745d8ca0bd3f4561a634c5403427ed34f5b","tid":1375492,"uid":31738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"歡迎理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61de2b1bd0e7ef20ad0e11254dfa033659fbade6","tid":1375492,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"等解放軍入城同黑警死過先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0763ba10de232d5214ceaffaa35d762b5b0b8d","tid":1375492,"uid":266274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zmDsLXC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzmDsLXC.jpg&h=9a821e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54965714